      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The franchise committee of the\ncity council will meet tonight and\ntake up several applications for fran\nchises which are now pending. The\napplications include that Of the\nWashington Gas a. Coke company. the\nOccur d'Alene & Spokane Electric\ncompany. Rufus Merriam and others\nfor an independent telephone fran\nchise and the two applications of the\nWashington Water Power company\nfor street car lines across the pro-\nposed Hangman creek bridge."
    }
